{"service_name": "Establish a Strategic Information Security Roadmap", "service_id": "4820674900131840", "company_name": "Corix Partners Technical Services Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Corix Partners Technical Services Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Establish a Strategic Information Security Roadmap\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    This service, from Corix Partners, defines and establishes an Information Security Strategic Roadmap across the organisation in order to ensure that the organisation is and remains appropriately protected.\r\n\r\nThe service applies to organisations where no structured Information Security Roadmap exists, or where Management believes it might be inadequate.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Meet with key business and IT stakeholders.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Review existing Information Security scope, strategy and relevant internal documentation.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Produce an independent summary of key strengths and weaknesses.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Produce independent recommendations to address immediate issues and improve effectiveness.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Validate conclusions and recommendations with Management.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Define the desired positioning and reporting lines for Information Security.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Aggregate into a proposed long-term vision for Information Security.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Define required short-term and mid-term objectives for Information Security.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Create an Information Security Strategic Roadmap based on previous steps.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Validate proposed Roadmap with Management and communicate to key stakeholders.\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Engagement with key stakeholders on Information Security across the organisation.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Focus on Security Strategy and Governance, not purely technical controls.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Service delivery driven by expert professionals with real-life field experience.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Focus on simplicity and common sense principles.\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a31000 to \u00a32000 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/585604/4820674900131840-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/585604/4820674900131840-sfia-rate-card-2015-04-28-1512.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/d